title: James Franklin explains his philosophy on toughness & building a culture
itunes:title: James Franklin explains his philosophy on toughness & building a culture
description:
DJ and Bucky are back with a special new episode. The guys talk with Penn State head football coach James Franklin on this podcast (2:07). They discuss a variety of topics with James Franklin including toughness, the importance of relationships, the best high school player he's ever seen, and how to build and maintain a culture.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
